<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/2 (Thu.) Taipei to issue fines for feeding wildlife/4 Signs Your Fast-Paced Life Is Killing You (Host:Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=566&amp;p=589#p589"><![CDATA[
12/2 (Thu.) Taipei to issue fines for feeding wildlife in parks/4 Signs Your Fast-Paced Life Is Killing You (Host: Larry)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a hybrid meeting on December 2 (Thursday):<br />On-site meeting:<br />If you have received at least one dose of vaccine, please join our physical meeting:<br />Dante coffee 丹堤(濟南店) 臺北市大安區濟南路25號 忠孝新生MRT Exit 3<br />On-line meeting:<br />If you haven’t gotten any vaccine or live far away from Taipei, please join our online meeting:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1<br /><br />Taipei to issue fines for feeding wildlife in parks<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.google.com.tw/search?q=Taipei+to+issue+fines+for+feeding+wildlife+in+park+&amp;authuser=0&amp;sxsrf=AOaemvLAOBeMwn7u9e2AMjL1kcY0R8Gd8w%3Adoes">http://www.google.com.tw/search?q=Taipe ... d8w%3Adoes</a><!-- m -->  <br /> <br />Questions<br />1.Do you think feeding wild animals is good or bad and why? How does this behavior affect the entire environment? <br />2.Should Taiwan completely ban the feeding of wild animals and why?<br />3.According to statistics, there are currently about 150,000 stray dogs and cats in Taiwan. Are you satisfied with current governments measures to deal with stray animal and why? Is there any way to make the stray cats and dogs disappear completely? But is it possible?<br />4.Does your living environment have stray animals? Have you heard of or been attacked or unpleasant things happen to you? <br />5.Do you have pets in your family? Can you share its advantages and disadvantages with us? <br /><br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2<br /><br />4 Signs Your Fast-Paced Life Is Killing You<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.allprodad.com/signs-fast-paced-life-killing-you/">https://www.allprodad.com/signs-fast-pa ... lling-you/</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions<br />1.What does “fast-pasted life” mean? Do you think this is a modern trend or not? Why?  <br />2.What are the pros and cons of a fast-paced or slow-paced life? Do you prefer a fast-paced or slow-paced life? Why? <br />3.Are you satisfied with your current pace of life and why? Do you think     24 hours a day is enough for you or not? Why?<br />4.Why do people in cities like to made life so fast and why? What do you think of the pace of life in Taipei? How does it compare with Hong Kong or other metropolises? <br />5.Do you know why people in country like to live a slow and leisurely life? <br /><br />P.S.<br />1.丹堤咖啡有100元低消喔!<br />2.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=37037">JuliaHo</a> — Sat Nov 27, 2021 11:05 pm</p><hr />
